Class PJLabel.PJLabelDefaults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.kevinarpe.papaya.swing.widget.PJLabel.PJLabelDefaults

    PJLabel

    public static final class PJLabel.PJLabelDefaults
extends Object
    Stores defaults for PJLabel.

    All instances of this class are fully immutable, thus thread-safe, and safe to store as static final constants.

    Author:
    Kevin Connor ARPE (kevinarpe@gmail.com)
    See Also:
    PJLabel.DEFAULTS, PJLabel.DEFAULTS_FOR_ICON_ONLY
